       fhir:documentation [ fhir:v "The MedicationRequest resources can represent a medication using either a code or refer to the Medication resource. When referencing Medication, the resource may be [contained](http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/references.html#contained) or an external resource. The server application **MAY** choose any one way or more than one method, but if an external reference to Medication is used, the server **SHALL** support the _include` parameter for searching this element. The client application must support all methods. For example, A server **SHALL** be capable of returning all medications for a patient using one of or both: `GET /MedicationRequest?patient=[id]` `GET /MedicationRequest?patient=[id]&_include=MedicationRequest:medication`" ] ;
